{"word":"G2769 - κεράτιον - kerátion - ker-at'-ee-on - Husk","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κεράτιον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kerátion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ker-at'-ee-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Husk</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"தவிடு - பால்வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. a little horn"},{"paragraph":"2. the name of the fruit of the carob tree"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G2768 - κέρας - kéras - ker'-as/2768\">G2768</a>; something <i>horned</i>, that is, (specifically) the <i>pod</i> of the carob tree: - husk.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}